Judul: Simulation of synthetic fingerprint generation using Petri nets
Abstrak: This study describes the generation process of a synthetic fingerprint using the Petri nets. The presented Petri net simulates this process, in general. Then, there are presented various initial markings which simulate a particular real-life scenario. The proposed Petri net could be used to make the creation process more understandable and also it gives some space for optimisation and parallelisation.
